<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>MICROSCOPIC DESCRIPTION:</div><div><span style="color:red;">Histologic type: </span><span style="color:black;">Papillary urothelial carcinoma, noninvasive</span></div><div><span style="color:red;">Histologic grade: High grade</span></div><div><span style="color:black;">Tumor configuration: papillary </span></div><div>Extent of invasion: Papillary noninvasive carcinoma</div><div>Urothelial carcinoma in situ: Absent </div><div><span style="color:red;">Peritumoral lymphovascular invasion: Absent</span></div><div>Perineural invasion: Absent </div><div><span style="color:red;">Margin:</span></div><div>Tumor base: Free of tumor   Presence of tumor element, with / without
finding of muscular invasion, <b><span style="color:red;">compiled from
the report of ___..</span></b></div><div>Muscularis propria in specimen: Included / Not included</div><div><span style="color:red;">Lymph nodes: Not assessed</span></div><div>Immunohistochemical study: </div><div><br/></div><div> (This case has been reviewed by two pathologists.)</div></en-note>      ]]>
