<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p><span style="font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;">No basal cells surrounding the neoplastic glands are demonstrated by <span style="color: #ff6600;">p63 and 34βE12</span>. The neoplastic glands are positive for <span style="color: #ff6600;">p504s.</span></span></p>
</div>
<div><br/></div>
<div><br/></div>
</div>
